query:
SELECT ds.id, ds.date, ds.employeeId, e.name as employeeName, 
       ds.targetedCustomers, ds.confirmedCustomers, ds.registeredCustomers,
       ds.servicesSold, ds.targetedByServices, ds.salesAmount, ds.soldServices,
       ds.status, ds.notes
FROM daily_stats ds
LEFT JOIN employees e ON ds.employeeId = e.id
WHERE e.name LIKE '%سماح%'
ORDER BY ds.date DESC
LIMIT 20;
